                        <TextView
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                            android:text="The local people of urgram valley believe that Lord Krishna plays Ras Leela with his friends here. It is also believed that that people with ardent devotion and faaith in Lord Krishna can hear the sound of flute or bansi.&#xA;&#xA;The Bansi Narayan temple was believed to be the place where Lord Narayana emerged from the underworld after defeating the deamon king Bali in his Vamana avatar.Bali requested for the protection of the Lord and so Lord Vishnu accompanied king Bali to the underworld, assuming the role.Shri Narada Muni suggested Mata Lakshmi to travel to the underworld on a full moon of the Shravan month and tie a Raksha sutra on king Baliâ€™s wrist."
                            android:textSize="15sp"
                            android:textColor="@color/black"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_marginLeft="10dp"
                            android:layout_marginRight="10dp"/>
