                                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                                android:layout_marginRight="10dp"
                                android:text="To reach Bansi Narayan Temple, you have to travel to Rishikesh. Rishikesh is well connected through trains and roads. The nearest airport is the Jolly Grant airport in dehradun which is 21Km away from Rishikesh. &#xA;Further we have to travel through NH7 to reach Bansi Narayan Temple. You may find direct buses and taxis from Rishikesh to Devgram. You have to travel 247Km by road to reach Bansi Narayan Temple. &#xA; &#xA;Some major towns on the way include Devprayag, Srinagar, Rudraprayag, Karnaprayag, Gopeshwar, Joshimath, Helang, Devgram. You may find many restaurants and hotels to stay in these places.&#xA;&#xA;The trek to Bansi Narayan temple begins at Devgram which is 12 to 15 km long. The Bansi Narayan temple is situated approx. 12 km from Kalpeshwar Mahadev temple, the last of Panch Kedar."
